{"type": "root", "attrs": {"type": "node", "context": "sop", "icon": "SOP/finalizewaves", "internal": "finalizewaves", "tags": "fluid, dynamics, lowlevel", "version": null, "namespace": null}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Finalize Waves"], "extent": [0, 19]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Imparts wave velocities to points in waveform geometry"], "extent": [130, 192]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This operation is used in the creation of Particle Fluid waves.  Given a \ngroup of points created from geometry affected by one or more \n", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/waveform", "type": "link", "text": ["Waveform"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/waveform.html"}, " operators, Finalize Waves sets appropriate \nvelocities for each point."], "extent": [192, 430]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["A Waveform operator\u2019s ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Output Wave Velocity Attributes"]}, " option must\nbe enabled in order for a subsequent Finalize Waves operator to have \nthe desired effect."], "extent": [430, 591]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The Waveform operator does not generate a volume of points on its own.\nOnce a surface has been modeled as desired using Waveform operators,\nusing ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/extrudevolume", "type": "link", "text": ["Extrude Volume"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/extrudevolume.html"}, " and then\n", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/pointsfromvolume", "type": "link", "text": ["Points From  Volume"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/pointsfromvolume.html"}, " will create a set of points that Finalize\nWaves can act on.  These points can then be used to create a\n", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/particlefluidobject", "type": "link", "text": ["Particle Fluid Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/particlefluidobject.html"}, " that behaves as a wave."], "extent": [591, 1015]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["Finalize Waves has no parameters.  All relevant information needed for\nimparting the appropriate point velocities is derived from previous\nWaveform operators.  This is accomplished by means of attributes created\nwhen a Waveform\u2019s ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Output Wave Velocity Attributes"]}, " option is enabled."], "extent": [1015, 1301]}, {"level": 1, "id": "related", "container": true, "type": "related_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [1301, 1310], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/waveform", "type": "link", "text": ["Waveform"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/waveform.html"}], "extent": [1310, 1342]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/particlefluidobject", "type": "link", "text": ["Particle Fluid Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/particlefluidobject.html"}], "extent": [1342, 1397]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/extrudevolume", "type": "link", "text": ["Extrude Volume"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/extrudevolume.html"}], "extent": [1397, 1439]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/pointsfromvolume", "type": "link", "text": ["Points From Volume"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/pointsfromvolume.html"}], "extent": [1439, 1488]}], "container": true}], "text": "Related"}], "title": ["Finalize Waves"], "summary": ["Imparts wave velocities to points in waveform geometry"]}